The derivatization of SEs and NSEs such as trimethylsilyl (TMS) derivatives have been used to derivatize the non-acylated hydroxyl groups (
;
;
). For example, Hali ń ski and Stepnowski (2013) determined the main NSEs extracted from
Nicotiana tabacum
